<h3>POST /api/ragpicker/rates</h3>
<div>
  Rating an user
</div>
<b>Resource URL </b>
<div>
http://ragpickers.herokuapp.com/api/ragpicker/rates
</div>
<b>sample request</b>
<div>
  curl --data "user_id=18&score=1.6&token=login_token" "http://ragpickers.herokuapp.com/api/ragpicker/rates"
</div>
